{"tid":909712,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"屌那星，好期待Gin Lee聽日嗰個林夕音樂會！！！","createTime":"2018-11-20T15:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T00:21:24.000Z","uid":178713,"like":58,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f67a01a83f8899cf48c9ce04786d18f0318c5847","tid":909712,"uid":178713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"「叱咤樂壇 x Gin Lee Music Suite - 咤夕」音樂會2018 將於11月21日在中環PMQ元創方舉行，歌手Gin Lee（李幸倪）將即場演繹多首由林夕填詞的經典歌曲，包括 《紅豆》、《至少還有你》 、《<span style=\"color: red;\">獻世</span>》等，更有林夕親自為Gin Lee挑選的曲目《你們的幸福》、《水百合》和《<span style=\"color: red;\">弱水三千</span>》。<br />\n<br />\n音樂會以「Suite」命名，原來是指林夕曲目，還呼應了主題－套房。 音樂會將佈置成一間睡房，配合柔和燈光尤如置身於Gin的房間，細味每首在Gin心中舉足輕重的林夕之作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAgqAJa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAgqAJa.jpg&h=5432ec51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個撚個都話Gin差首好歌，空有唱功無用武之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日個音樂會就一次過唱曬啲正到仆街嘅歌俾你哋聽！！！仲要各類風格嘅歌都囊括曬，要 K歌有 K歌，要玩味有玩味，劍走偏鋒去到國語經典，一次有齊，正撚到括約肌鬆弛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好想知Gin唱藥水三千會係點</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d9c286f25665fd3e1eac85e5a241d2da7659fc","tid":909712,"uid":178713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6938c540f8629e58e29811b59da281df2fa1f75b","tid":909712,"uid":171901,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"唱功一般"},{"pid":"8702d10a9a81e44ec41d364a8e13cf26fb346656","tid":909712,"uid":178713,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6938c540f8629e58e29811b59da281df2fa1f75b","tid":909712,"uid":171901,"like":1,"dislike"